import React, {useState} from "react"
import {Box, Button, Flex} from "rebass"
import {
  Label,
  Input
} from '@rebass/forms'
export default () => {

  return (<Box>
 <Box width={1/3} px={2}>
      <Label htmlFor='name'>Name</Label>
      <Input
        id='name'
        name='name'
        defaultValue='Jane Doe'
      /></Box>
  </Box>)
}
